156
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,680
That woman is dangerous.

157
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,160
Yeah.

158
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,530
Maybe you shouldn't go.

159
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,480
Why is she looking for you?

160
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,410
She has clues about Zixi's murder.

161
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:09,100
She has clues about my sister.

162
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,610
I'll go with you.

163
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,250
Yes, let's go together.

164
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,680
Let's go.

165
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:16,000
Go.

166
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,680
Go, go.
